<h1>Start Up Issue</h1>
@* <p> you can set the app settings key "StartupIssue" = true in order to reproduce a startup issue</p>
<p> You can enable ASPNETCORE_DETAILEDERRORS=true in app service configuration/app settings to enable detailed error in the page </p> </>
<h1></h1>
<p>you can set the app settings key "StartupIssue" = coldStart60  or "StartupIssue" = coldStart240</p>
<p>  in order to reproduce a cold start issue (it will take 2min to fail with 500.37) </p>
<p>HTTP Error 500.37 - ASP.NET Core app failed to start within startup time limit</p>
<h1></h1> *@


<div class="accordion" id="accordionExample">
    <div class="accordion-item">
        <h2 class="accordion-header">
            <button class="accordion-button" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseOne" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapseOne">
                Startup Error
            </button>
        </h2>
        <div id="collapseOne" class="accordion-collapse collapse show" data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
            <div class="accordion-body">
                Set the app settings key  <strong> "StartupIssue" = true. </strong> in order to reproduce a startup error
                <p></p>
                <img src="~/images/startupError.png" class="img-fluid">
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="accordion-item">
        <h2 class="accordion-header">
            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseTwo" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseTwo">
                Cold Start
            </button>
        </h2>
        <div id="collapseTwo" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
            <div class="accordion-body">
                <p>   set the app settings key  <strong> "StartupIssue" = coldStart60 </strong> to reproduce a cold start of 60 sec </p> 
                <p>   set the app settings key  <strong> "StartupIssue" = coldStart240 </strong> to reproduce a cold start of 240 sec </p>
               
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="accordion-item">
        <h2 class="accordion-header">
            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseThree" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseThree">
                Enable Detailed Errors
            </button>
        </h2>
        <div id="collapseThree" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
            <div class="accordion-body">
                Enable   <strong> ASPNETCORE_DETAILEDERRORS=true</strong> in app service configuration/app settings to enable detailed error in the page
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

